  "detailed_description": "In a topdown perspective you control the candy girl, a young woman who loves candy.<br />\r\nYou will enter a frantic battle against the Yballs, they are clay monsters, and<br />\r\ninvaded the world to steal the candy.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nUse your super powers and your rifle to destroy your enemies. You will be able to<br />\r\nuse several different types of projectiles, shoot mercilessly.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nYou will face small, big and giant enemies, some of them will shoot you, others<br />\r\n will explode on you like a bomb. You will also encounter obstacles on the way, <br />\r\nsuch as cannons, birds, and many bombs. Be careful.",
  "about_the_game": "In a topdown perspective you control the candy girl, a young woman who loves candy.<br />\r\nYou will enter a frantic battle against the Yballs, they are clay monsters, and<br />\r\ninvaded the world to steal the candy.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nUse your super powers and your rifle to destroy your enemies. You will be able to<br />\r\nuse several different types of projectiles, shoot mercilessly.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nYou will face small, big and giant enemies, some of them will shoot you, others<br />\r\n will explode on you like a bomb. You will also encounter obstacles on the way, <br />\r\nsuch as cannons, birds, and many bombs. Be careful.",
